{"tid":1630253,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"now記者著火一定係警察臥底做","createTime":"2019-10-06T11:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:04.000Z","uid":73959,"like":59,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"317e86a67f770990a30d4fb4d3166fc3f769f372","tid":1630253,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"首先我向受傷記者送上最深切的慰問<br />\n<br />\n前線示威者係有用火魔法<br />\n但每次都掉唔中黑警<br />\n<br />\n相反<br />\n黑警受過訓練<br />\n次次都瞄人個頭<br />\n仲針對記者<br />\n<br />\n你可以話係手足誤中<br />\n但都可以話係黑警假扮示威者做<br />\n<br />\n學警妓余乜春講<br />\n我哋重點應該放係警察喬裝示威者<br />\n多次被影到掉汽油彈<br />\n因此有合理理由懷疑係卧底做"},{"pid":"3c373572db759b357e6bec524b5b8cfb6c278dbc","tid":1630253,"uid":73959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:55:09.000Z","msg":"咁快有負評證明我講中咗"},{"pid":"8e76cd5fd7a8ebe4f91d9766af7db0be3f050012","tid":1630253,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e00a3f99d8e7ea26a0a9fc14fd0686e67aa3b12","tid":1630253,"uid":73959,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:59:41.000Z","msg":"當唔知係手足定黑警做嘅時候<br />\n梗係話對方啦<br />\n因為黑警做嘅話一樣都會話返係示威者做<br />\n仲講咩道唔道德？<br />\n何況冇人知係咪真係手足誤中"},{"pid":"a9ffe9ea3f7f3ac3debe474b9269a04ec7b1d90b","tid":1630253,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:01:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">日後要小心</span>"},{"pid":"fb80f06bbe9539bf4c5bd01bc722322641d95b38","tid":1630253,"uid":68868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:01:28.000Z","msg":"好撚煩 你話人掟 人地否認<br />\n依家一係冷處理 一係say sorry"},{"pid":"4e8f14d7c6d27cf5aaa0fa182ee66c546c0776bb","tid":1630253,"uid":37719,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":